{"tid":2140571,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"馮睎乾 ： 戴耀廷不要自滿，你即使贏了，中共也沒有輸，這就是傳說中的「雙贏」","createTime":"2020-08-05T05:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T08:14:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":88,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b3ea71b0cdecf93f465f6083c9e78ded8fa2d362","tid":2140571,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:48:12.000Z","msg":"馮睎乾 ：<br />\n戴耀廷不要自滿，你即使贏了，中共也沒有輸，這就是傳說中的「雙贏」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/2MEFGNEFG5ERJNSAOCGNPHC7JY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2F2MEFGNEFG5ERJNSAOCGNPHC7JY%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zeam9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=32cecc8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2F2MEFGNEFG5ERJNSAOCGNPHC7JY%2F&h=fad0d7d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/2MEFGNEFG5ERJNSAOCGNPHC7JY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n35+完成了，然後呢？ - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8-gjHXEArGQxX_SSPXY3J78Q4Zk=/6648x4398/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3BK27XABRNEEDEW73AXP2HZCUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8-gjHXEArGQxX_SSPXY3J78Q4Zk%3D%2F6648x4398%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3BK27XABRNEEDEW73AXP2HZCUA.jpg&h=da4b2249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「政治發明家」戴耀廷在〈35+已超額完成〉說，35+初衷是「透過取得立法會過半議席，令當權者必須做出最後的決定，或是正面回應港人的政治訴求，或是再加大打壓的力度。」若中共選擇後者，結果就是「引入國安法、推翻選舉、成立臨時立法會」，勢必「招來國際社會的嚴厲制裁，或有可能促使中共退讓。」現在中共已加速達到35+目標，所以戴耀廷說是「超額完成」。細想確有道理，不能說是精神勝利。<br />\n<br />\n有點常識的人都知道：即使抗爭派在立法會過半，北京也決不讓你當家作主，終究還是開外掛來DQ、釋法、搞臨立會。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。因此，戴耀廷不要自滿，你即使贏了，中共也沒有輸，這就是傳說中的「雙贏」。<br />\n<br />\n我雖然估到個流程，但估唔到個速度。35+忽然達標了，然後呢？戴耀廷說，「未來一年，中共必會再加大打壓的力度，我們必須咬緊牙關捱過去⋯⋯抗爭力量更重要做的，是重整力量，紮穩已建立起的社區網絡」。但要為時代巨變做好準備，我們不能只務外而不修內。<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"large\">你想改變政權，政權會說你犯法，但你要革自己的命，沒人能判你有罪。</span></span>古往今來一切社會進步，都不是靠弱者推動的。努力變強，提升境界，free yourself，就是現在最應該做的事。<br />\n<br />\n李登輝的神師卡萊爾在《衣裳哲學》說過。。。。。。。。。。。。。該明白你所追求的東西，已經和你一起，除了這裏，就不在任何地方。但願你看得到！」"},{"pid":"a3e5e77341d65932718815d3ff23916e73b8e0cd","tid":2140571,"uid":30084,"like":7,"dislike":50,"score":-43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:51:09.000Z","msg":"林夕之後蘋果又出一隻內鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱狗又搞戴教授"},{"pid":"b222bc9618f95439f1bc809315cfca38af7bc3b1","tid":2140571,"uid":30084,"like":4,"dislike":39,"score":-35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:51:14.000Z","msg":"林夕之後蘋果又出一隻內鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱狗又搞戴教授"},{"pid":"6e3e29d8b368a797cee5b62e0d29d8918e5783b0","tid":2140571,"uid":30084,"like":2,"dislike":36,"score":-34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:51:32.000Z","msg":"林夕之後蘋果又出一隻內鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱狗又搞戴教授"},{"pid":"7063272de655ffd5b9156ae24872fe1ede87c477","tid":2140571,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:54:42.000Z","msg":"孟德拉和孔子都說過：「不獨裁，毋寧死。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2242fde71f1f07937d497a6b55bce6da0cb2444b","tid":2140571,"uid":48631,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"quote":{"pid":"6e3e29d8b368a797cee5b62e0d29d8918e5783b0","tid":2140571,"uid":30084,"like":2,"dislike":36,"score":-34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:51:32.000Z","msg":"林夕之後蘋果又出一隻內鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱狗又搞戴教授"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:55:27.000Z","msg":"其實佢冇屌戴耀廷喎，佢係認同戴耀廷嘅講法，但只不過補多句就係35+超額完成，都唔等於中共有咩損失"},{"pid":"cffd3eb03af81d62d9b86adbe821464d0499dea9","tid":2140571,"uid":55089,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"2242fde71f1f07937d497a6b55bce6da0cb2444b","tid":2140571,"uid":48631,"like":59,"di